title: VR Youtube 3D Videos FULL v67.0 APK [SadeemPC]
description:
VR Youtube 3D Videos FULL v67.0
Requirements: Android 4.1 and up

VR YouTube 3D allows for the viewing of YouTube videos with a compatible VR viewer. Voice control is activated with the magnet when viewing 2D videos from YouTube.	

To search any video, simply pull the magnet and a mic will appear. Say the name of the video and the best result will be played automatically. To scroll through the list,simply use the command "next", or "back" to go back. "reset" will sync videos, and "play" will play. ZOOM in or out any video by SWIPING up or down accordingly. VR YouTube 3D can also open external YouTube links from a browser. When prompted with choices from a web-browser, choose normal mode to play a regular YouTube video side by side, or 3D to play SBS videos.

There can be a lag between the time each video loads, leading to a lack of sync. When this occurs, simply doubletap the screen to pause both videos, and doubletap again to resume viewing.
